ow/topics/social-good-lists"><img src="http://6.mshcdn.com/follow/images/default_topic_32x32.png" alt="Social good lists" /></a><div class="content"> <a class="topic_title" href="/follow/topics/social-good-lists">Social good lists</a> 0 followers</div><a class="follow_obj_link follow_link" href="/follow/topics/social-good-lists/follow">Follow</a></li></ul><script type="text/javascript">setupTopics();</script><hr /><h6>For more <a href="/social-good/">Social Good</a> coverage</h6><ul id="for_more"><li class='twitter'> <a href="http://twitter.com/socialgood">Follow Mashable Social Good</a></li><li class='facebook'> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/socialgood">Become a fan on Facebook</a></li><li class='rss'> <a href="http://feeds.mashable.com/mashable/socialgood">Subscribe to the Social Good channel</a></li><li class='downloads'> Download our free apps for <a href="http://mashable.com/2010/08/02/mashable-android-app/" rel="nofollow">Android</a>, <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mashable-for-mac/id412390413?mt=12" rel="nofollow">Mac</a>, <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mashable/id356202138?mt=8" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">iPhone</a> and <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mashable-for-ipad/id370097986?mt=8" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">iPad</a></li></ul> </footer> </article> <section class="section list clearfix more-in"><h1 class='bar'><span>More Stories in Social Good</span></h1><ol class="rectangle_posts "><li class="post rectangle e0 t0 ct0 "><div class="image-frame"> <a class="img" href="http://mashable.com/2011/03/02/bill-gates-ted-talk/"> <img src="http://4.mshcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/360bill.jpg" width="125" alt="Bill Gates Talks About Knowledge Revolution at TED [LIVE BLOG]" /> <span class='overlay'></span> </a></div><div class="stories"><h2 class="entry-title"> <a href="http://mashable.com/2011/03/02/bill-gates-ted-talk/" rel="self bookmark" class='headline' title="Permanent Link to Bill Gates Talks About Knowledge Revolutio